      <title>加拿大人口增长创纪录，但未来增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/population-gains-in-canada-set-record-but-slower-growth-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大的人口增长率创下新纪录，为全球最大的移民计划之一达到最高速度的一年画上了句号，因为总理贾斯汀·特鲁多政府面临着减缓未来移民流入的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/population-gains-in-canada-set-record-but-slower-growth-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:37:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穿越英国的移民数量激增，削弱了苏纳克的誓言</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/migrant-boat-crossings-to-uk-surge-undercutting-sunak-vow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年前三个月乘船抵达英国的移民人数创下历史新高，削弱了首相里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)在为本已艰难的竞选活动做准备时做出的核心承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/migrant-boat-crossings-to-uk-surge-undercutting-sunak-vow</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:32:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
